271&ndash;347.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash; (ed.), 2005, <em>The Church and Galileo:
Religion and Science</em>, Notre Dame: University of Notre Dame
Press.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2009, &ldquo;The Galileo Affair: Two
