<li>Moss, Jean Dietz, 1993, <em>Novelties in the Heavens</em>,
Chicago: University of Chicago Press.</li>

<li>Naylor, Ron, 2007, &ldquo;Galileo&rsquo;s Tidal Theory.&rdquo;
<em>Isis</em>, 98 (1): 1&ndash;22.</li>

