<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2003, &ldquo;Mental Models in
Galileo&rsquo;s Early Mathematization of Nature,&rdquo; <em>Studies in
History and Philosophy of Science Part A</em>, 34: 229&ndash;264.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2004, &ldquo;The Cognitive Development of
Galileo&rsquo;s Theory of Buoyancy,&rdquo; <em>Archive for the History
