<li>Shapere, Dudley, 1974, <em>Galileo: A Philosophical Study</em>,
Chicago: University of Chicago Press.</li>

<li>Shapin, Steven, 1996, <em>The Scientific Revolution</em>, Chicago:
University of Chicago Press.</li>

<li>Shea, William R., 1972, <em>Galileo&rsquo;s Intellectual
