451&ndash;483.</li>

<li>Valleriani, Matteo, 2010, <em>Galileo Engineer</em>, Dordrecht:
Springer.</li>

<li>van Dyck, Maarten, 2005, &ldquo;The Paradox of Conceptual Novelty
